  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: 0f832b14936fc2048824d9308b14ded6, type: 3}
  m_Name: DateMenu
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: 
  allLines:
  - side: 2
    characterName: Counselor
    characterSprite: {fileID: 0}
    sentence: "Alright champ, you\u2019re good to go with all the controls, right?
      Not gonna lie the navigator stick is sick, I\u2019ll never get over how smooth
      this new version is. Hehe heh..heh..."
    eventTrigger: 
    choices: []
  - side: 2
    characterName: Counselor
    characterSprite: {fileID: 0}
    sentence: ... okay enough yapping, ahem. The menu on your screen contains all
      the items that are available to order.
    eventTrigger: 
    choices: []
  - side: 2
    characterName: Counselor
    characterSprite: {fileID: 0}
    sentence: "You can see all the allergies and food sensitivities listed if you
      just hover over the items. And if you wanna put in an order, just drag the
      item into one of the daters\u2019 slots! Easy peasy."
    eventTrigger: 
    choices: []
  - side: 3
    characterName: Chaperon
    characterSprite: {fileID: 0}
    sentence: "\rYeah, I understand. And, I order accordingly to their profiles,
      correct? My notes were right... um, where are my notes?\r\n"
    eventTrigger: 
    choices: []
  - side: 2
    characterName: Counselor
    characterSprite: {fileID: 0}
    sentence: "See I wasn\u2019t being silly when I told you to read those profiles
      real carefully. You gotta memorize!"
    eventTrigger: 
    choices: []
  - side: 3
    characterName: Chaperon
    characterSprite: {fileID: 0}
    sentence: "But... why? Wouldn\u2019t it be a safer bet if I could just, take
      a peek at their profiles?"
    eventTrigger: 
    choices: []
  - side: 2
    characterName: Counselor
    characterSprite: {fileID: 0}
    sentence: "Think of it as a test honey, we need to know if you\u2019re actually
      paying attention to the daters or not. Can\u2019t just blindly trust you to
      be attentive just because you give off \u201Cgood vibes\u201D."
    eventTrigger: 
    choices: []
  - side: 3
    characterName: Chaperon
    characterSprite: {fileID: 0}
    sentence: Damn, okay. Good thing I did read the profiles properly then. I think..
      Shit.
    eventTrigger: 
    choices: []
  - side: 2
    characterName: Counselor
    characterSprite: {fileID: 0}
    sentence: "Woah! Language! You\u2019re on the clock missy! Heh, just kidding
      say whateverrr, I don\u2019t give a ****. Just don\u2019t cuss directly to
      the daters, m\u2019kayy? M\u2019kay."
    eventTrigger: 
    choices: []
  - side: 2
    characterName: Counselor
    characterSprite: {fileID: 0}
    sentence: "You\u2019re on your own for now, be quick with the orders though \u2018cause
      that Marsian is getting kinda fidgety. It\u2019s making even me nervous."
    eventTrigger: "Men\xFCMiniGame"
    choices: []
  nextScenario: {fileID: 0}
